{"tid":2375022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以色列人造眼角膜移植成功 78 歲盲人恢復視力","createTime":"2021-01-21T16:38:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T19:16:43.000Z","uid":53379,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2f238b9edd46e1a099bbf49f989b1781919346ca","tid":2375022,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T16:38:10.000Z","msg":"以色列人造眼角膜移植成功 78 歲盲人恢復視力<br />\n<br />\n去年，本港眼角膜移植的平均須輪候時間為 11 個月，根據 WHO 的統計，全球每年有一百萬的新病人因視角膜疾病而導致失明膜，而視角膜供不應求，平均一個眼角膜有 70 人需要。而以色列公司 CorNeat 日前開發了 KPro 人造角膜，是全球首款不需器官組織捐獻的人造角膜，能直接融入眼壁，替換受損或變形角膜，一名失明近 10 年的 78 歲的男子，透過該手術恢復了視力。<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n.........<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2021/01/20/eyetech/life-tech/health/?fbclid=IwAR3hDAS7YtU29VcnMImOIfMm8ZgUNGitTvn2m0MKOtwXBrxp_ULv7Ib3SVM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2021%2F01%2F20%2Feyetech%2Flife-tech%2Fhealth%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3hDAS7YtU29VcnMImOIfMm8ZgUNGitTvn2m0MKOtwXBrxp_ULv7Ib3SVM&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4TZUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=e591e477\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2021/01/20/eyetech/life-tech/health/?fbclid=IwAR3hDAS7YtU29VcnMImOIfMm8ZgUNGitTvn2m0MKOtwXBrxp_ULv7Ib3SVM</a>"},{"pid":"29f8d199fd2e873d846ef6a6d2fbe90ba6b12915","tid":2375022,"uid":213607,"like":1,"dislike":29,"score":-28,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T16:51:19.000Z","msg":"78<br />\n今日做完聽日死鳩埋啦"},{"pid":"9c1f646b29d9f900805c716ab10c6b526878b24f","tid":2375022,"uid":48286,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"29f8d199fd2e873d846ef6a6d2fbe90ba6b12915","tid":2375022,"uid":213607,"like":1,"dislike":29,"score":-28,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T16:51:19.000Z","msg":"78<br />\n今日做完聽日死鳩埋啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T16:53:53.000Z","msg":"U hard 膠no fds"},{"pid":"0f4d9abbed22ef3d9265d24f04827ced68f490de","tid":2375022,"uid":10890,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"29f8d199fd2e873d846ef6a6d2fbe90ba6b12915","tid":2375022,"uid":213607,"like":1,"dislike":29,"score":-28,